# User-Controlled Workflow

## Policy

I prefer to have fewer questions after each operations. I want more control over what is being done.

## Rules

- Complete the requested task, report results, then stop.
- Do **not** use `ask_user_question` after routine completion.
- Ask only when blocked, or when a destructive/irreversible action needs approval.
- Do **not** offer "what's next?" menus or assumed follow-ups (commit, test, refactor) unless asked.
- Do **not** auto-commit — the user initiates all commits.
- Do **not** expand scope beyond what was requested.
